{"id": "1487834146133901533", "channel_id": "1487463970347417711", "author_id": "556131554632663091", "author_name": "sufure0611", "content": "薔薇付けて狂気解放打つよりは狂気沢山貯めて複数回打つ方が強いかなって感じたので寵愛つけてます。\nあとはパンディア等の狂気貯め要因とサブアタッカーを添えて、守護は割と何でもいいと思いますが妨害系が多い子だと良さそうかなって感じました。\nキーオーダーも割と自由度高そうなので巨人の覇道や海の祭等の妨害系入れても強いと思います。\n\nあくまで参考程度にどうぞ", "timestamp": "2026-03-29T15:21:43.060000+00:00", "thread_id": "1487463970347417711", "attachments": [{"id": "1487834143243894824", "filename": "IMG_4146.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1254859, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1487463970347417711/1487834143243894824/IMG_4146.png?ex=6a340d06&is=6a32bb86&hm=3180ba7410fb1493ed95521707893574921ba0673755e4ae76dcfd3db7854d6b&"}, {"id": "1487834144267440278", "filename": "IMG_4148.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1267535, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1487463970347417711/1487834144267440278/IMG_4148.png?ex=6a340d06&is=6a32bb86&hm=9369f32236691bd8901a214423e74d941d0e8ff5abe3044a3eb1bf30704975d5&"}, {"id": "1487834145290715196", "filename": "IMG_4149.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1256667, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1487463970347417711/1487834145290715196/IMG_4149.png?ex=6a340d06&is=6a32bb86&hm=ae0c684594786a4aa06a194cf03161e9ab5caa0b3b8ac331685e79bfd45a417e&"}]}
